---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import MarketingPageLayout from '../layouts/MarketingPageLayout.astro';
import aboutPhoto from '../assets/about-photo.jpg';
import { withBase } from '../lib/paths';
---

<MarketingPageLayout title="About" description="About Elm City Photography.">
  <section class="relative -mx-4 h-[60vh] overflow-hidden">
    <Image
      src={aboutPhoto}
      alt="Couple on coastal cliffs for Elm City Photography"
      width={853}
      height={1280}
      class="h-full w-full object-cover"
      loading="eager"
    />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-green-deep/35"></div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto mt-14 max-w-2xl px-4 pb-16">
    <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-muted">About Elm City Photography</p>
    <h1 class="mt-2 text-5xl">OUR STORY</h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-lg leading-8 font-semibold">
      Founded in New Haven, Elm City Photography is built around the belief that modern portraiture should feel graceful,
      intimate, and deeply personal from first hello to final edit.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-sm leading-7 text-muted">
      <p>
        We are drawn to unguarded glances and quiet spaces — the moments in between the posed portrait and the candid smile.
        Our sessions are guided by light, connection, and storytelling, with locations chosen to match each couple’s rhythm.
      </p>
      <p>
        For each engagement and graduation session we keep the process calm and collaborative, allowing you to
        move with the day instead of moving to the camera. That approach lets the photos reflect who you are, not just
        how you looked in front of a lens.
      </p>
      <p>
        We photograph what matters most: your laugh line, the glance at the same pace as the wind, and the way joy fills the
        frame when people are present with one another. Every edited photo is handled with careful color, balanced contrast,
        and a refined, editorial finish inspired by the natural landscape of New England.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our work balances natural portraiture with elegant composition, offering timeless imagery that feels lived-in, cinematic,
        and unmistakably yours.
      </p>
    </div>
    <a
      href={withBase('/contact/')}
      class="mt-8 inline-flex text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-green-deep underline decoration-green-mid underline-offset-4"
    >
      Get in Touch →
    </a>
  </section>
</MarketingPageLayout>
